04/22/2009 - News restarted. Starting from today, the most important development will be described here, again.

02/06/2008 - NOSE moved to SourceForge.net. Lapack 95 needs to be downloaded separately.

10/24/2007 - version 0.5.3 - QME module is partially working

03/05/2007 - version 0.5.2 - calculates fluorescence spectrum

02/21/2007 - version 0.5.1 - this version is able to calculate first order polarization and the linear
			 absorption spectrum. Program is MPI parallel and uses a new configuration file format.
			 
01/15/2007 - version 0.5.0 - starting point of a MPI parallel version of NOSE



